verbose_text: In addition, following supplementation of the culture medium with various concentrations of KCl, the results indicated that, with increasing KCl concentration, the amount of C-peptide secreted by beta islet like cells derived from miR-32-infected HuAECs was much greater than that secreted by cells derived from miR-Mut-infected HuAECs (XREF_FIG and XREF_TABLE).
